.SH NAME
component_add \- register a component
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" component_add
.BI "(struct device *dev "  ","
.BI "const struct component_ops *ops "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
component device
.IP "ops" 12
component callbacks
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Register a new component for \fIdev\fP. Functions in \fIops\fP will be called when the
aggregate driver is ready to bind the overall driver by calling
\fBcomponent_bind_all\fP. See also \fIstruct component_ops\fP.

The component needs to be unregistered at driver unload/disconnect by
calling \fBcomponent_del\fP.

See also \fBcomponent_add_typed\fP for a variant that allows multipled different
components on the same device.
